1
00:00:21,840 --> 00:00:23,260
♪Wandering alone♪

2
00:00:23,260 --> 00:00:25,540
♪Walking far by dusk-lit streets♪

3
00:00:25,540 --> 00:00:27,430
♪Your eyes are as cold as clouds♪

4
00:00:27,430 --> 00:00:28,970
♪Faintly coming into view♪

5
00:00:28,970 --> 00:00:30,360
♪The city lights♪

6
00:00:30,360 --> 00:00:32,630
♪Lit up that single moment♪

7
00:00:32,630 --> 00:00:36,140
♪I can't hide or stop missing you♪

8
00:00:36,140 --> 00:00:37,640
♪I can't forget those moments♪

9
00:00:37,640 --> 00:00:39,280
♪Losing you♪

10
00:00:39,610 --> 00:00:41,320
♪Like the seasons in my memory♪

11
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:43,290
♪Without winter♪

12
00:00:43,290 --> 00:00:44,920
♪Walking down the long, dark street♪

13
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:46,460
♪Snow will never fall again♪

14
00:00:46,460 --> 00:00:48,200
♪Our old story was torn♪

15
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:50,610
♪Into scattered pieces♪

16
00:00:50,610 --> 00:00:53,430
♪Replaying every single scene♪

17
00:00:53,430 --> 00:00:55,980
♪After you left♪

18
00:00:57,530 --> 00:01:00,510
♪As if our documentary♪

19
00:01:00,510 --> 00:01:03,120
♪Lost winter♪

20
00:01:04,770 --> 00:01:07,180
♪The breeze speaks of good times♪

21
00:01:07,180 --> 00:01:11,080
♪Pure white devotion♪

22
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:13,990
♪Send out a letter♪

23
00:01:14,300 --> 00:01:17,780
♪Carrying my longing♪

24
00:01:17,780 --> 00:01:20,980
=The Double Game=

25
00:01:21,020 --> 00:01:23,940
=Episode 15=

26
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:25,480
Let me make this clear:

27
00:01:26,350 --> 00:01:27,310
Not a chance.

28
00:01:31,710 --> 00:01:32,550
What?

29
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:34,240
What did you say?

30
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:38,350
Believe me. I'll kill her right now.

31
00:01:40,540 --> 00:01:42,020
(File transfer)

32
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:42,880
Fine.

33
00:01:43,040 --> 00:01:43,880
Do it.

34
00:01:49,950 --> 00:01:51,870
I really will do it.

35
00:01:51,870 --> 00:01:52,950
(Lu Tingxiao)

36
00:01:52,950 --> 00:01:54,070
Do it now.

37
00:01:54,950 --> 00:01:56,150
Do you want me to count?

38
00:01:59,510 --> 00:02:00,350
Three.

39
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:07,400
Two.

40
00:02:10,740 --> 00:02:12,660
(File transfer)

41
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:14,200
One.

42
00:02:14,540 --> 00:02:16,460
(File transfer.)

43
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:25,520
What?

44
00:02:26,150 --> 00:02:26,990
Too scared?

45
00:02:37,430 --> 00:02:39,360
You will not even save your woman.

46
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:41,800
Lu Tingxiao,

47
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,240
do you even count as a man?

48
00:02:48,190 --> 00:02:49,560
Let me make this clear today.

49
00:02:50,870 --> 00:02:51,910
She is not my woman.

50
00:02:53,710 --> 00:02:55,400
I have never liked her.

51
00:02:56,590 --> 00:02:57,430
Also,

52
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:59,430
don't use such dirty tricks

53
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:00,360
to threaten me again.

54
00:03:01,870 --> 00:03:03,870
Especially not with her.

55
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:09,560
(So, I am not worth threatening you?)

56
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:23,190
This is the choice he gave you.

57
00:03:45,700 --> 00:03:47,860
(Lianxin Island Feasibility Report)

58
00:03:48,910 --> 00:03:51,240
(So, Lu Jianchuan used fake papers)

59
00:03:51,750 --> 00:03:54,679
(Payback period: about 9.5 years)
(to disguise the commercial residence)

60
00:03:54,750 --> 00:03:56,630
(and get the construction permit.)

61
00:03:58,120 --> 00:04:00,120
(Who was bold enough to fake this?)

62
00:04:02,820 --> 00:04:05,340
(Led by Luhai Real Estate
Development Company)

63
00:04:08,820 --> 00:04:14,260
(Applied by: Fang Lanxin;
Approved by: Fang Changru)

64
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:47,520
Are you okay?

65
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:49,040
Did you run into anyone or anything

66
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:50,000
strange today?

67
00:04:50,870 --> 00:04:52,270
Like a kidnapping?

68
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:55,640
Kidnapping?

69
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:57,560
Who would kidnap me?

70
00:04:58,390 --> 00:04:59,323
You're overthinking it.

71
00:05:00,270 --> 00:05:01,110
Or do you mean

72
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:03,360
you want me taken away?

73
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:05,830
That's not what I meant.

74
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:07,560
I'm just worried about you.

75
00:05:08,190 --> 00:05:09,030
Thanks.

76
00:05:09,510 --> 00:05:11,070
I'm tired. I'll head back and rest.

77
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:17,160
What happened to your hand?

78
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:20,750
I just slipped and fell.

79
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:23,400
Show some respect.

80
00:05:24,510 --> 00:05:25,680
Don't get all grabby here.

81
00:05:26,213 --> 00:05:27,513
It won't look good if we're seen.

82
00:05:29,430 --> 00:05:30,270
Wait.

83
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:34,680
What happened to your neck?

84
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:36,640
I'm fine.

85
00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:37,590
Let me see.

86
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:43,000
I told you I wasn't kidnapped.

87
00:05:47,070 --> 00:05:47,910
Lu Tingxiao,

88
00:05:48,830 --> 00:05:49,920
don't worry at all.

89
00:05:50,830 --> 00:05:53,720
No one will ever use me against you.

90
00:06:15,270 --> 00:06:16,110
Check everything

91
00:06:16,270 --> 00:06:17,430
Lin Zhi'er did after leaving

92
00:06:17,510 --> 00:06:18,436
the beauty salon today.

93
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:19,870
Don't miss a single detail.

94
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,920
This is the choice he gave you.

95
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,270
Let's go. Move!

96
00:06:51,430 --> 00:06:52,680
Dear, are you okay?

97
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:54,630
Hurry and untie me.

98
00:07:04,830 --> 00:07:05,670
It's okay now.

99
00:07:30,510 --> 00:07:32,070
Your wrists are all red.

100
00:07:32,510 --> 00:07:33,463
I got you some medicine.

101
00:07:33,880 --> 00:07:35,106
Let me put some ointment on it.

102
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:45,400
I'm sorry.

103
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:46,870
I got there too late.

104
00:07:47,870 --> 00:07:48,823
I didn't keep you safe.

105
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,720
How did you know I was there?

106
00:07:53,630 --> 00:07:55,270
Lin Yuqing texted me and said

107
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:57,430
you went into the beauty salon
with a man,

108
00:07:58,190 --> 00:07:59,030
so I went over

109
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:01,200
to catch you.

110
00:08:01,397 --> 00:08:02,550
But I didn't catch anything.

111
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:05,360
I knew they were up to no good.

112
00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:08,880
What happened next?

113
00:08:09,630 --> 00:08:10,870
I was about to leave,

114
00:08:11,070 --> 00:08:12,000
but I saw you

115
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:13,950
being dragged into a van.

116
00:08:14,070 --> 00:08:14,920
So, I followed them.

117
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:18,720
Why did you risk yourself to save me?

118
00:08:19,730 --> 00:08:20,570
I know

119
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:21,750
I used to be a real jerk,

120
00:08:22,390 --> 00:08:23,230
but please trust me.

121
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:25,230
To me, you're my wife.

122
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,830
I can't let you get hurt.

123
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:33,080
Isn't Yu Qiaoqiao your true love?

124
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:34,960
True love?

125
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:36,790
She was after my money.

126
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:39,030
I've completely cut ties with her.

127
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:44,560
Can you

128
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,790
forgive the old me

129
00:08:47,510 --> 00:08:48,440
and accept who I am now?

130
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:50,960
I promise you

131
00:08:51,550 --> 00:08:52,480
I'll keep you safe.

132
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,080
I want you to stop

133
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:12,360
everything you're doing,

134
00:09:12,510 --> 00:09:13,720
get out of Luzhou Group,

135
00:09:13,910 --> 00:09:14,790
and go abroad at once.

136
00:09:16,190 --> 00:09:17,523
(Lu Tingxiao)
She's not my woman.

137
00:09:18,390 --> 00:09:20,150
I have never liked her.

138
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:22,600
Don't use such dirty tricks

139
00:09:22,670 --> 00:09:23,510
to threaten me again.

140
00:09:25,030 --> 00:09:27,030
Especially not with her.

141
00:09:27,030 --> 00:09:28,260
(Lu Tingxiao)

142
00:09:29,030 --> 00:09:29,960
(Lu Tingxiao,)

143
00:09:30,870 --> 00:09:33,000
(you won't take my wife again.)

144
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:45,960
Xu Wangzu!

145
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:01,590
Mr. Lu, what's wrong?

146
00:10:08,630 --> 00:10:09,750
Come with me.

147
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:46,800
Lu Tingxiao,

148
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:48,720
what are you doing? Are you crazy?

149
00:10:49,670 --> 00:10:51,000
Who gave you the nerve

150
00:10:51,270 --> 00:10:52,360
to kidnap my woman?

151
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:53,840
What are you saying?

152
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:54,960
What kidnapping?

153
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:56,040
I have no idea.

154
00:10:59,790 --> 00:11:00,670
If you don't talk,

155
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:02,870
I'll keep hitting till you do.

156
00:11:07,630 --> 00:11:08,579
If you lay a hand on me,

157
00:11:08,630 --> 00:11:10,360
my sister and her husband
won't let you go.

158
00:11:12,790 --> 00:11:14,270
You don't have to admit it.

159
00:11:15,390 --> 00:11:16,390
Tell them this:

160
00:11:16,870 --> 00:11:18,240
I'm keeping score on this.

161
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:19,800
Get lost.

162
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:28,440
Mr. Lu, your hand.

163
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,080
Let me take care of it.

164
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:36,480
Why did you betray me?

165
00:11:38,870 --> 00:11:39,710
Mr. Lu.

166
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:48,670
You told Lu Jianchuan
she was at the beauty salon,

167
00:11:49,240 --> 00:11:50,080
right?

168
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:52,670
I'm sorry, Mr. Lu.

169
00:11:54,120 --> 00:11:56,000
I didn't know they meant
to kidnap Ms. Lin.

170
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:59,030
Chairman Lu caught something
on my family.

171
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:00,870
- I...
- Go.

172
00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:02,550
I don't need you anymore.

173
00:12:03,390 --> 00:12:04,230
Mr. Lu.

174
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:07,200
Everyone has their own struggle.

175
00:12:07,910 --> 00:12:09,320
I believe you were forced into it.

176
00:12:10,270 --> 00:12:11,600
I also believe you meant no harm.

177
00:12:15,320 --> 00:12:17,200
But when you tipped them,

178
00:12:17,390 --> 00:12:19,150
you knew something would happen.

179
00:12:20,750 --> 00:12:22,240
That was your choice.

180
00:13:08,386 --> 00:13:09,375
Your wound hasn't healed.

181
00:13:09,386 --> 00:13:10,659
Let me put some ointment on you.

182
00:13:10,670 --> 00:13:11,510
No, thanks.

183
00:13:12,080 --> 00:13:13,120
I can handle it myself.

184
00:13:15,565 --> 00:13:16,712
About yesterday's kidnapping,

185
00:13:16,723 --> 00:13:17,603
I thought it was fake.

186
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:19,120
So, I said those things.

187
00:13:19,750 --> 00:13:20,750
No need to explain.

188
00:13:22,870 --> 00:13:23,710
Wen Yan,

189
00:13:24,073 --> 00:13:25,000
I thought you were safe

190
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:26,060
at the beauty salon.

191
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:27,270
So, I said those things.

192
00:13:27,390 --> 00:13:28,710
- Fine.
- I do care for you.

193
00:13:28,750 --> 00:13:30,120
Fine, I get it.

194
00:13:32,240 --> 00:13:34,000
If you don't believe me,
ask Qing and Bai.

195
00:13:35,246 --> 00:13:36,532
Does it matter if I believe you?

196
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:39,480
We were never in the same world.

197
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:41,670
You have too many secrets.

198
00:13:42,270 --> 00:13:43,870
I have my own life to deal with.

199
00:13:44,790 --> 00:13:46,390
If we can't be honest,

200
00:13:47,390 --> 00:13:48,670
let's just end this.

201
00:13:50,960 --> 00:13:51,800
No.

202
00:13:52,480 --> 00:13:54,080
This won't end just like that.

203
00:13:54,630 --> 00:13:56,600
What are you doing, Lu Tingxiao?

204
00:13:56,750 --> 00:13:57,590
Let go of me.

205
00:13:58,360 --> 00:13:59,200
Let go.

206
00:14:00,110 --> 00:14:00,980
What are you doing?

207
00:14:00,990 --> 00:14:02,256
- Let go.
- What are you doing?

208
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:03,160
Let go of me.

209
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:04,040
Let go.

210
00:14:09,380 --> 00:14:11,049
How dare you go
after your sister-in-law?

211
00:14:11,120 --> 00:14:11,960
Have you no shame?

212
00:14:13,670 --> 00:14:14,510
Lu Tingyu,

213
00:14:14,750 --> 00:14:15,590
look closely.

214
00:14:15,720 --> 00:14:16,720
Is she your wife?

215
00:14:18,200 --> 00:14:19,040
What are you saying?

216
00:14:19,270 --> 00:14:20,120
She is my wife.

217
00:14:20,750 --> 00:14:21,590
Lu Tingyu,

218
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:22,720
didn't you notice

219
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:24,240
that your wife of years

220
00:14:24,390 --> 00:14:25,320
was someone else?

221
00:14:25,480 --> 00:14:26,320
Lu Tingxiao!

222
00:14:28,870 --> 00:14:29,710
Tingyu,

223
00:14:30,030 --> 00:14:30,870
stop pretending.

224
00:14:31,059 --> 00:14:32,358
That day at the memorial service,

225
00:14:32,510 --> 00:14:33,720
you saw Wen Yan

226
00:14:33,910 --> 00:14:35,510
talking with Lin Zhi'er in the lounge.

227
00:14:36,120 --> 00:14:37,240
You've long found out

228
00:14:37,630 --> 00:14:38,910
that Wen Yan isn't your wife.

229
00:14:43,720 --> 00:14:44,840
What about our mom?

230
00:14:45,670 --> 00:14:46,510
I don't know either.

231
00:14:48,390 --> 00:14:49,630
She may have died long ago.

232
00:14:50,320 --> 00:14:51,790
(No wonder she's changed so much.)

233
00:14:52,270 --> 00:14:53,720
(So, she was never Lin Zhi'er.)

234
00:14:59,240 --> 00:15:00,080
You really

235
00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:02,150
knew all along?

236
00:15:02,960 --> 00:15:03,800
I...

237
00:15:04,720 --> 00:15:05,560
I...

238
00:15:06,550 --> 00:15:07,390
Yes.

239
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:09,160
I knew all along

240
00:15:09,870 --> 00:15:10,830
you weren't Lin Zhi'er.

241
00:15:12,120 --> 00:15:13,106
I didn't say it outright

242
00:15:13,150 --> 00:15:13,990
because I realized

243
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:15,266
I've fallen for who you are now.

244
00:15:15,440 --> 00:15:16,720
I want a fresh start with you.

245
00:15:17,910 --> 00:15:18,750
Wen Yan,

246
00:15:19,080 --> 00:15:20,550
give me a chance, okay?

247
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:23,160
You two...

248
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:25,510
You two are insane.

249
00:15:26,150 --> 00:15:26,990
Wen Yan.

250
00:15:27,360 --> 00:15:28,200
Lu Tingxiao,

251
00:15:28,360 --> 00:15:29,200
don't forget

252
00:15:29,910 --> 00:15:31,630
she's still my wife in name.

253
00:15:33,120 --> 00:15:34,390
Even you said it's only in name.

254
00:15:35,150 --> 00:15:37,240
She never accepted you in her heart.

255
00:15:38,870 --> 00:15:39,710
Lu Tingxiao,

256
00:15:39,960 --> 00:15:41,560
don't forget that when she was in danger

257
00:15:41,630 --> 00:15:42,790
and needed help the most,

258
00:15:43,000 --> 00:15:44,113
I was the one who saved her,

259
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:45,560
not you, the man

260
00:15:45,630 --> 00:15:46,870
who coldly told her to die

261
00:15:47,080 --> 00:15:48,550
when she was kidnapped.

262
00:16:06,840 --> 00:16:08,290
♪This door♪

263
00:16:08,690 --> 00:16:13,440
♪Lets in the sky outside♪

264
00:16:13,920 --> 00:16:17,480
♪With a voice even lighter♪

265
00:16:17,480 --> 00:16:20,290
♪Than how you just greeted me♪

266
00:16:20,740 --> 00:16:22,110
♪I know now♪

267
00:16:22,440 --> 00:16:27,320
♪What the chill in my body means♪

268
00:16:27,670 --> 00:16:30,540
♪The moment salt hits the wound♪

269
00:16:30,740 --> 00:16:34,160
♪My heart still beats so naively♪

270
00:16:34,330 --> 00:16:37,320
♪To complete♪

271
00:16:37,780 --> 00:16:41,530
♪A joy that needs no brave pretense♪

272
00:16:41,670 --> 00:16:44,170
♪How cruel sincerity can be♪

273
00:16:44,310 --> 00:16:47,860
♪Like a door with no key♪

274
00:16:48,170 --> 00:16:50,490
♪Maybe you just passed by♪

275
00:16:50,490 --> 00:16:54,070
♪The tears in my eyes♪

276
00:16:54,780 --> 00:16:57,330
♪You looked like you had nothing to say♪

277
00:16:57,330 --> 00:16:59,070
♪Then got so good at being cold♪

278
00:16:59,070 --> 00:17:01,910
♪That's why a smile feels so precious♪

279
00:17:02,120 --> 00:17:04,210
♪Maybe you just passed by♪

280
00:17:04,360 --> 00:17:08,690
♪The tears burned into my heart♪

281
00:17:09,070 --> 00:17:11,360
♪Let's say silence was just for show♪

282
00:17:11,360 --> 00:17:16,030
♪Even if I've grown another year♪
